.TH "ClipEdit" "" "" "" ""
.hy
.SH Brief
.PP
The main goal of the \f[B]ClipEdit\f[] project is to manipulate cliparts
to edit, highlight and customize images in a user\-friendly way.
.SH Features
.PP
ClipEdit comes with a set of features to help you customize, edit or
draw attention to specific parts of your document.
Every widget at your disposal is fully movable, scalable and editable so
you can always open and edit your document in the future without the
need of starting over.
.PP
Let\[aq]s review the different features at your disposal.
.SS Text boxes
.PP
Simple text boxes to add quotes, notes or huge text walls wherever you
want to.
.SS Numbered bubbles
.PP
Add a set of numbered bubbles on top of your document to facilitate the
explanation of multi\-steps actions.
.SS Arrows
.PP
A set of arrows to help you point and focus on crucial information.
Different styles and shapes are available.
.SS Cliparts library
.PP
Import and place images or icons all over the place !
.SS Charts
.PP
Create charts in your document by entering a set of data.
.SS Shapes
.PP
Add basic and scalable shapes to your document.
Each shape comes with a shape of vertex you can use to manipulate it.
.PP
Available shapes:
.IP \[bu] 2
Rectangles
.IP \[bu] 2
Triangles
.IP \[bu] 2
Circles
.SS Layers
.PP
Create sophisticated documents using layers.
